modules.description: Provides operations for fetching, building, testing, and deploying code based on version control events. Works with Git repositories, commit hashes, and build artifacts. Used to automate continuous integration workflows and update status reports on pull requests.

Parses ANSI escape sequences from input strings, converting them into styled HTML output. Maintains internal state to handle incomplete sequences across multiple calls. Generates colorized terminal output suitable for rendering in web environments.
